        Sales Highlights
        Sign Up To Newsletter  |  Gift Cards  |  OFFTHERECORD.NET

        Welcome to Phonica Records' digital gift cards page.


        • This is a digital gift card or voucher that allows you to buy anything on the site*. The card or voucher comes via email to an address of your choosing, with a unique code that can only be used once.
        • We sell electronic gift cards in denominations of £10, £25, £50, £75, £100 or £250. You can mix and match or buy multiple vouchers to get to the amount you want to spend. However, you can redeem ONLY one gift card per one checkout transaction. Once purchased, the gift cards cannot be exchanged for a denominal constituting their added values (e.g. 2 x £25 gift cards cannot be exchanged for a single £50 gift card). You do not have to use the whole amount in one transaction though - your credit continues until all is used for the gift card.
        • You can personalise the gift card with your message and have it sent immediately upon completion of the order. If it's for a gift for a future date, we advise you to get the unique code sent to your own email address.
        • To redeem your voucher, add items to your cart on our site, proceed to the checkout stage, on the final payment screen you will be able to enter your unique gift voucher code in the box provided. All gift cards are non-refundable. There is a 3 year expiry date on all vouchers.
        • We also sell traditional, physical gift vouchers for use at our store at 51 Poland St, London. These can be purchased and redeemed in the store but cannot be used on the website. However, if you do want to use them on the site, or want to use digital gift cards in the store, its best to contact us at the address below and we can work something out.
        • If you have any queries or problems regarding our digital gift cards please contact customerservice@phonicarecords.com for assistance.

        *The gift cards or vouchers can only be used at www.phonicarecords.com, on any goods except Technics decks, additional gift vouchers or tickets. We reserve the right to add further exemptions on particular items in the future.
